column11: Lord Ahmad was out in Sydney, Australia with his family on a personal holiday. He undertook a 1 day visit to Canberra, Australia, to hold Aviation Security meetings, with his counterparts on the Department's behalf. The only cost to the Department was the car used to pick Lord Ahmad up from his holiday home in Sydney to Canberra and the return journey.
